# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:9
translate portuguese dana2_5cfb9131:

    # "It's a fairly normal day of work. I work in Mrs. Mills office all day."
    "É um dia de trabalho bastante normal. Passo o dia todo no escritório da Sra. Mills."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:10
translate portuguese dana2_85a4b54e:

    # "Cleaning all the normal things."
    "A fazer as tarefas habituais."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:12
translate portuguese dana2_f50e7708:

    # "Typing all normal stuff."
    "A digitar as coisas de sempre."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:13
translate portuguese dana2_d80566b6:

    # "Work passes quickly and I'm busy the entire time."
    "O tempo passa depressa e estou ocupada o tempo todo."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:16
translate portuguese dana2_1dfeab57:

    # bs "Thanks for all your help today, [pcname]. You did good work today."
    bs "Obrigada por toda a sua ajuda hoje, [pcname]. Fez um bom trabalho hoje."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:17
translate portuguese dana2_e8ce3674:

    # pc "Thank you Mrs. Mills."
    pc "Obrigada, Sra. Mills."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:18
translate portuguese dana2_ed5736f0:

    # bs "I'm going to stay around a little later. You have a good evening."
    bs "Vou ficar por aqui um pouco mais. Tenha uma boa noite."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:19
translate portuguese dana2_dd07e1d2:

    # pc "Okay, you too Mrs. Mills."
    pc "Está bem, para si também, Sra. Mills."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:20
translate portuguese dana2_fe768c71:

    # "I leave her office and start walking down the hall towards the lobby."
    "Saio do escritório dela e começo a caminhar pelo corredor em direção ao átrio."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:25
translate portuguese dana2_e92ba526:

    # "Dana's voice stops me in my tracks. She's arguing with somebody on the phone and sounds upset."
    "A voz da Dana faz-me parar. Ela está a discutir com alguém ao telefone e parece chateada."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:26
translate portuguese dana2_1edbfb68:

    # "I don't really mean to eavesdrop, but I also don't want to just walk in on their conversation, so I lean against the wall and wait."
    "Não é minha intenção ficar a ouvir, mas também não quero simplesmente intrometer-me na conversa deles, por isso encosto-me à parede e espero."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:27
translate portuguese dana2_506f8528:

    # cw "I'm sorry. I'm just like ten minutes late, but I'm coming home soon, I promise."
    cw "Desculpa. Estou só uns dez minutos atrasada, mas vou para casa em breve, prometo."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:28
translate portuguese dana2_594beb0b:

    # "There is a pause. I can hear a voice on the other side of the phone yelling, but I can't make out the words."
    "Há uma pausa. Consigo ouvir uma voz do outro lado do telefone a gritar, mas não consigo perceber as palavras."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:29
translate portuguese dana2_29f965e7:

    # cw "I try to! It's not that easy. I can't just leave my work half-finished."
    cw "Eu tento! Não é assim tão fácil. Não posso simplesmente deixar o meu trabalho a meio."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:30
translate portuguese dana2_011812d0:

    # "Her voice drops and catches in her throat."
    "A voz dela abaixa e fica presa na garganta."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:31
translate portuguese dana2_3ae30315:

    # voice dana_trying
    # cw "I'm trying. I'm sorry."
    voice dana_trying
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:33
translate portuguese dana2_8788608a:

    # cw "No, I'm not cheating on you. I don't know how many times I have to tell you that."
    cw "Não, não te estou a trair. Não sei quantas vezes tenho de te dizer isso."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:34
translate portuguese dana2_d0c4854a:

    # "More yelling comes from the phone receiver."
    "Mais gritos vêm do auscultador."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:35
translate portuguese dana2_b30f69a4:

    # cw "That's fine. I'll see you tonight then."
    cw "Tudo bem. Então vejo-te esta noite."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:37
translate portuguese dana2_e7265cb4:

    # "She hangs up the phone and there's a bang as she slams it against the desk."
    "Ela desliga o telefone e ouve-se um estrondo quando ela o atira contra a secretária."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:38
translate portuguese dana2_494fc925:

    # "After a moment, I peek around the corner and see her leaning over with her head buried in her hands, her shoulder shaking as she sobs."
    "Passado um momento, espreito pela esquina e vejo-a debruçada com a cabeça enterrada nas mãos, o ombro a tremer enquanto soluçava."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:39
translate portuguese dana2_a3b7daec:

    # "I probably should just stay out of it, but I can't help it."
    "Provavelmente devia simplesmente não me meter, mas não consigo evitar."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:40
translate portuguese dana2_ca8447bf:

    # "I can't stand to see her upset like this. I have this overwhelming urge to fix things."
    "Não suporto vê-la assim tão perturbada. Sinto uma vontade irresistível de resolver as coisas."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:43
translate portuguese dana2_f041e4b8:

    # "I walk up to her desk and put my hand gently onto her shoulder."
    "Aproximo-me da secretária dela e coloco a mão gentilmente no ombro dela."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:44
translate portuguese dana2_fa75bbc3:

    # pc "Are you okay?"
    pc "Estás bem?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:46
translate portuguese dana2_3619d1fa:

    # "She lifts her head and quickly wipes away her tears."
    "Ela levanta a cabeça e enxuga rapidamente as lágrimas."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:47
translate portuguese dana2_a3f56836:

    # voice dana_justfine
    # cw "Yeah, everything's just fine."
    voice dana_justfine
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:49
translate portuguese dana2_a794c62f:

    # pc "I sort of overheard your conversation."
    pc "Acabei por ouvir a vossa conversa."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:50
translate portuguese dana2_a97815ff:

    # cw "Oh, did you?"
    cw "Ah, sim?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:51
translate portuguese dana2_efb33164:

    # "She stays silent for a moment, obviously trying to calm herself down."
    "Ela fica em silêncio por um momento, obviamente a tentar acalmar-se."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:54
translate portuguese dana2_391aa753:

    # "Then suddenly everything seems to burst and she wraps her arms around my waist and buries her face into my stomach."
    "Então, de repente, tudo parece explodir e ela envolve-me a cintura com os braços e enterra o rosto na minha barriga."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:55
translate portuguese dana2_458c8244:

    # voice dana_sofrustrated
    # cw "I'm sorry, [pcname]. I'm just so frustrated with all of it."
    voice dana_sofrustrated
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:57
translate portuguese dana2_8921cee5:

    # "I put a hand on her back and rub gently as she cries into my shirt."
    "Coloco uma mão nas costas dela e esfrego-lhe suavemente as costas enquanto ela chora na minha camisa."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:58
translate portuguese dana2_77fb0dd9:

    # "After a couple minutes of sobbing, she starts to calm down again and she pulls back away from me."
    "Após alguns minutos a soluçar, ela começa a acalmar-se novamente e afasta-se de mim."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:61
translate portuguese dana2_213acdac:

    # cw "I'm sorry. I got your shirt wet."
    cw "Desculpa. Molhei a tua camisa."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:62
translate portuguese dana2_45a788d3:

    # pc "It'll dry. Feeling better now?"
    pc "Vai secar. Sentes-te melhor agora?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:63
translate portuguese dana2_5c9ff614:

    # "She nods."
    "Ela acena com a cabeça."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:64
translate portuguese dana2_3bb01968:

    # cw "Better. Not great, but better."
    cw "Melhor. Não ótima, mas melhor."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:65
translate portuguese dana2_f02c67f3:

    # cw "I'll figure everything out. I'll get my work done faster and get home earlier, so he won't be mad at me."
    cw "Vou resolver tudo. Vou terminar o meu trabalho mais depressa e chegar a casa mais cedo, para que ele não fique zangado comigo."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:66
translate portuguese dana2_6831ff3c:

    # pc "If you need anybody to talk to, I'm here okay?"
    pc "Se precisares de alguém com quem falar, estou aqui, está bem?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:67
translate portuguese dana2_0518d8da:

    # cw "Thanks, [pcname]. You're so sweet."
    cw "Obrigada, [pcname]. És tão querido."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:68
translate portuguese dana2_786b3b21:

    # voice dana_beokay
    # cw "I'll be okay though. I'll see you tomorrow, okay?"
    voice dana_beokay
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:70
translate portuguese dana2_d8858bda:

    # pc "Want me to stay and help with anything?"
    pc "Queres que fique e te ajude em alguma coisa?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:71
translate portuguese dana2_af71dcbc:

    # cw "That's okay. I got it. Thank you though, really."
    cw "Não é preciso. Eu trato disto. Mas obrigada, a sério."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:72
translate portuguese dana2_859c6cd6:

    # pc "Okay, well I'll see you tomorrow then."
    pc "Está bem, então vejo-te amanhã."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:73
translate portuguese dana2_0507fc22:

    # "I give her a final pat on her shoulder before turning and walking outside. I hope she'll be okay. It's a lot to deal with."
    "Dou-lhe uma última palmada no ombro antes de me virar e sair. Espero que ela fique bem. É muita coisa para lidar."

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:74
translate portuguese dana2_2199c3c0:

    # "I walk through the cool night and get in my car."
    "Caminho pela noite fresca e entro no meu carro."

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:2
    old "Dana has been running late getting home from work."
    new "A Dana tem chegado tarde do trabalho."

    # game/Scenes/Dana/dana2.rpy:3
    old "This scene will happen automatically a few days after the previous scene."
    new "Esta cena vai acontecer automaticamente alguns dias depois da cena anterior."

